snippet.title: unprompted - announce trailer
snippet.description:
Guess the words used to create A.I. images!

Unprompted is OUT NOW on Steam!
💻 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2129130/Unprompted/ 💻

Play the web game now! Three new images, every day: 
🧠 https://unpromptedgame.com 🧠

___

Unprompted is a project by Matt Eshleman, an architect currently based in Shanghai.

Unprompted is neither wholly human-made, nor wholly A.I.-generated. As such, the designer takes sole responsibility for the content of these games.

Images were generated with Craiyon.

info@unpromptedgame.com

___

Music:
Atmosphere Fragment by Clacksberg
